<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n03015b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n03" href="#n03015b">N03 (VI.B.3)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n03all.htm#n03015b"> 15(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> contrition / attrition (Si D) </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: <i>Contrition</i>: true sorrow for sin, being motivated by love of God. <i>Attrition</i>: imperfect sorrow for sin, being due to fear of punishment. &lsquo;Si D&rsquo; is Simon Dedalus. </mm> </dd></dl>
